      "span_text": "The one-and two-photon absorption spectra of the twisted porphyrin series reproduce the qualitative features of the experimental spectra, including the increase of the two-photon absorption cross-section upon extending the monomer into a dimer. 63 In addition, the computed maximum two-photon absorption cross sections semiquantitatively reproduce the values observed experimentally."
